# API-Football (api-sports.io) — structured football data for fetch_form / fetch_h2h.
# 1. Create a FREE account at https://www.api-football.com/  (no credit card)
# 2. Copy your key from the dashboard.
# 3. Copy this file to ".env" (which is gitignored) and paste the key below.
#
# Free plan = 100 requests/day. A full backfill is ~48 form + 72 h2h calls, so
# run form one day and h2h the next, or spread them out. Without a key the
# fetchers fall back to the (less reliable) DuckDuckGo scrape automatically.
API_FOOTBALL_KEY=your_key_here

# The Odds API (the-odds-api.com) — bookmaker 1X2 odds for the market anchor
# (fetch_odds.py -> data/market_odds.csv -> "מול בוקמייקרים" dashboard view).
# 1. FREE account (~500 requests/month, no card): https://the-odds-api.com
# 2. Paste your key below. Without it the anchor stays dormant (nothing breaks).
ODDS_API_KEY=your_key_here
